text: Hans Zurbriggen (22 February 1920 - 23 July 1950) was a Swiss ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1920 births Category:1950 deaths Category:Swiss male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Switzerland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:People from Valais
